WILLIAMS v. WARDEN OF MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 2,

September Term, 1962 (Adv.).]

Decided May 18, 1962.

Before Bruñe, C. J., and Hammond, Prescott, Horney, Marbury and SybErt, JJ.

PER Curiam.

For the reasons stated by Judge J. DeWeese Carter for dismissing the petition, the application for leave to appeal is denied.

Application denied.
